		)
		(uuid "70c4eb42-4a9b-4c13-b197-70ddb626f282")
	)
	(text "Gate drive network for STP20NM60FP:\n- Vdrive = 15 V (from IR2136)\n- Series gate resistor Rg = 15-22 Ω\n- Internal MOSFET gate resistance Rint ≈ 1.6 Ω\n- Total gate charge Qg ≈ 40-50 nC\n- Target switching ~100 ns → Ig ≈ 0.5-0.7 A\n- Optional diode for asymmetrical turn-on/off (ON slower, OFF faster)\n- Purpose: Limit di/dt, reduce ringing/EMI, protect driver, comply with IEC\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 243.078 184.15 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "73077aff-cdb5-453b-9b79-113262ca7331")
	)
	(text "470pF + 1kΩ ITRIP Filte\nτ = RC = 1kΩ × 470pF = 470ns\nt_rise (10-90%) ≈ 1.0μs\nt_90 (settling) ≈ 1.1μs\nf_cutoff = 1/(2πRC) = 339kHz"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 116.332 169.164 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(face "Times New Roman")
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(color 128 128 128 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "a1e903ea-1f22-4a07-b650-d66d2583a382")
	)
